The layout is made by spelworm and after v2 the lightning and textures are made by idm 


The outdoor part is with a sidewall u can walk on and camp and in the middle u got towers u can camp in and on.
The indoor part has 5 barricade rooms and 2 rooms where u can camp on boxes there also 2 'secrets' in there but they aren't to hard to find
There is a vent indoor wich will lead to 2 more rooms
